---
title: Greek-Style Feta & Oregano Lamb Steak with Roasted Potatoes
description: A warm bed of golden potatoes makes the perfect base for a mouth-watering lamb steak with all the trimmings. Tender strips of lamb leg steak are covered in caramelised onions, oregano and snowflakes of crumbled feta. Now, if that doesn't sound like heaven on earth, we don't know what does!
